    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at Gradation 1 per the MRL 2 requirements table. Uncertainty quantification has been performed and confirms RH < 1 at the 95th percentile of the characterised input variability space. The overall evidence package is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
